{
  "text": "Finally, we'll launch EC2 instances using our launch template. We're launching one instance in each public subnet for high availability. The instances will automatically get public IP addresses because we set map-public-ip-and-launch to true on the public subnets. Each instance uses the launch template we created, which includes the AMI instance type, security groups, and user data. Once launched, these instances will be accessible via HTTP on port 80 from the internet, thanks to our security group configuration. The sensors can also access MASOs through the NMAM eligibility.",
